# Maintenance, Care, and Troubleshooting

## Maintenance
- Check wiring regularly (especially button and power connections)
- Make sure SD card is properly inserted in MP3 module
- Keep Arduino powered with stable supply

## Care
- Do not press button repeatedly during cooldown
- Avoid exposing electronics to moisture
- Secure all components to prevent movement

## Troubleshooting

### Button not working
- Check wiring to input pin
- Make sure pull-up/pull-down is correct

### Lights not turning on
- Check relay/transistor connection
- Verify power source for lights

### Audio not playing
- Confirm SD card is inserted
- Make sure file is named correctly (ex: 0001.mp3)
- Check TX/RX wiring

### System not responding
- Restart Arduino
- Re-upload code
